<h4>Portland Attorneys</h4>
<p>Johnston Law Firm, P.C. is a respected Portland personal injury law firm. We represent clients throughout Oregon 
who have been injured or killed due to the negligence of another. We represent individuals and their families 
against dangerous drivers, negligent hospitals and physicians, corporations who endanger consumers, insurance 
companies who wrongfully deny and underpay claims, and other entities and individuals who violate the societal 
safety rules which keep the public safe. We are a trial law firm for real people and our primary mission is 
ensuring justice for our clients, and safety in our community.</p>
<h2>We Handle Your Car Accidents</h2>
<p>Car accidents happen in the blink of an eye. Injuries can be horrible and life-altering. 
Once you receive the medical care needed, it's important to work with an experienced <a href='https://johnston-lawfirm.com/attorneys/marc-a-johnston/'
car accident attorney </a> to evaluate your legal options. </p>
